column5: HTHM stopped in over night on his way home.  We got out this morning for some Bass. It was a short day because Albert was anxious to get home after a week on the road. We caught a bunch and lost a few on plastic toads, but we really did okay with 4 inch senko-type worms...
Nice mini_g2g.  Those are some ofc worthy bass!
Awesome !!! Good to see you guys got out for some.
As usual, A good time was had by all. Thanks for your hospitality Garry!
